OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy cloud to start on
OL,6,FWednesday, with perhaps the odd spot
OL,7,Fof light rain. Becoming dry into the
OL,8,Fafternoon, with cloud breaking to give
OL,9,Fsunny spells. A slight breeze,
OL,10,Fparticularly along the coast, but
OL,11,Ffeeling mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry through the evening and
OL,14,Fovernight. Clear skies seeing the
OL,15,Fdevelopment of some low cloud, mist
OL,16,Fand fog by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
