OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FEarly low cloud, mist and
OL,6,Ffog clearing to leave a dry, bright
OL,7,Fand mild afternoon. Cloud thickening
OL,8,Finto the evening however, bringing
OL,9,Fsome outbreaks of rain to end the day.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRain
OL,12,Fovernight Thursday into Friday,
OL,13,Fclearing into the day to give some
OL,14,Fsunshine. A colder night into
OL,15,FSaturday. Conditions becoming cloudier
OL,16,Fand milder into the weekend, with some
OL,17,Flight rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
